quilibrium the \\emph{richest} group (having maximum expected utility per\nperson) covers a constant fraction of the total volume.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Apr 2012 05:38:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 30 Jan 2013 05:02:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-01-31"}
