s in\nsparse random subsets.\n  Balogh, Morris and Samotij have independently obtained related results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Apr 2012 11:11:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 2 Jul 2012 19:29:10 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 28 Nov 2014 10:13:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-12-01"}
